{
  "stem": "24364.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You could hear everything that was going on, you could-- the first time I saw sex or heard sex, which was not very pleasant, I can tell you that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there we stayed for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- the sanitary conditions were terrible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The food was lousy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Water was insufficient.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was really bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I remember we had some-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some provisions which we brought from Bratislava, which we were keeping obviously for a time that it was absolutely necessary to add something to what we were getting.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But I remember one day we were so hungry, so that I decided-- I had a box of cookies which my parents had sent me to Bratislava, which was probably three-- three months or four months old.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But I decided with a friend of mine, well, to hell with it, let's eat those cookies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I opened the box.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I looked-- when we looked at the box, it was full with worms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what we did-- we were so hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went to a corner which was very dark, and it was very easy to find on that boat, and we ate those cookies.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll never forget that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very good, even though they were full with worms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nothing really detrimental happened to us from the cookies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But otherwise, the sanitary conditions on the ship were really very bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And quite a few people started getting sick and started with diarrhea and high fever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were already starting to murmur about, you know, typhoid or dysentery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I myself got sick once.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was-- I got a high fever and diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
